est iterating over phases |\\n| `FullyCondensed` as redundant state | N/A | Not redundant -- justified by the `handler.condensed` transient check and the performance skip |\\n| `ActionClearEndedAt` name vs behavior | Low | Acceptable; document as tech debt to revisit if more fields are added |\\n| Defensive `&& Phase == PhaseEnded` guard | N/A | Good practice, keep |\\n| Stringly-typed code | N/A | None found |\\n\\nThe two test consolidation suggestions are the actionable items. The production code changes are clean and well-motivated.\"}],\"totalDurationMs\":94912,\"totalTokens\":65301,\"totalToolUseCount\":17,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1142,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":61197,\"output_tokens\":2961,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":1142,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"61b81f4c-03f3-41ab-a847-eaf1a43815f8\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"012c4fa5-b7a4-4b14-ad92-1afdd69e90c5\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"db57b693-b4f5-47da-9cc5-651e9169ac1d\",\"version\":\"2.1.63\",\"gitBranch\":\"skip-fully-condensed-sessions\",\"slug\":\"cozy-napping-bachman\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"message\":{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-01T20:13:01.260Z\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01NfYt4LmrpdMhZzKHRzjDMc\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01LnWzPCYmASbQjPSzwbrJXv\",\"name\":\"Grep\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"other\\\\.txt\",\"path\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli/cmd/entire/cli/strategy\",\"output_mode\":\"content\",\"-n\":true,\"glob\":\"*_test.go\"},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\